answersResultList.title: Mariah Carey.
answersResultList.resultContent: You don't just sing. No, you grab each note and twist it into submission. You're beautiful but complicated, intentionally murky about your past, and living in the moment. Perhaps there's a wee problem hidden under your facade, which might explain those loose-cannon utterances and mysterious breakdowns. Plus, you have a thing about sparkly objects, which is kinda cute.

answersResultList.title: Christina Aguilera.
answersResultList.resultContent: Maybe you had a hard childhood and/or some lucky breaks. But now that you found your voice, you gotta be you. For those who believe your story, you inspire them to overcome their own hardships. For those who think you're just another showoff, you flaunt your talents - because everyone knows they'd kill for what you have now.

answersResultList.title: Katy Perry.
answersResultList.resultContent: With some leftover outfits from the girl you used to be and input from your insane genius friends in the sound booth, you morphed into a bizarre, sexy, attention-grabbing cartoon character-like diva. Your outrageous jokes are so on point that nobody knows if they should take you seriously. At least you keep 'em laughing for all the right reasons.
